MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2008-0582. State v. Silverman.

Montgomery App. No. 22097, 176 Ohio App.3d 12, 2008-Ohio-618, 889 N.E.2d 1034. On motion to clarify court judgment. Motion granted. Cause remanded to the court of appeals to consider appellee’s remaining assignments of error.
